Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.88,0:00:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的目标 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:11.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大富豪 巴特拉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.28,0:00:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的? 当然是「Greed Island」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.43,0:00:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要如此执着于这个游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.31,0:00:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说您已经花费了相当大的金额了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.89,0:00:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 这是爱啊 爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.95,0:00:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜爱的东西想独占是很正常的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.90,0:00:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱是?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.09,0:00:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社会上有很多传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.58,0:00:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对要抓住金的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\bord0\c&H000000&\pos(960,956.25)\fscy120}拍卖{\c&H0148F9&} × {\c&H000000&\fscy120}和{\c&H0148F9&} × {\c&H000000&\fscy120}焦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.63,0:02:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在几点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.67,0:02:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷拉皮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.15,0:02:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下午两点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然睡了半天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是整整两天 酷拉皮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.02,0:02:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板呢 地下竞拍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终还是中止了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说剩下的商品会在后天放到网上拍卖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板也接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一直期待着参加拍卖会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:54.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会这么容易就罢休的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:02:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史库瓦拉被杀掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽莎因此伤心欲绝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.92,0:03:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍到的「火红眼」也被他们夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.14,0:03:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但比起这个 老板因为艾丽莎的事受到了打击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后自己说要回去...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杰和奇犽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.31,0:03:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们很精神 现在...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.19,0:03:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们正在做自己该做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以现在你也要好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:45.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来的是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.90,0:03:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦幻游戏 「Greed Island」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:04:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我们来看下这个软件的神奇力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如各位所见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.57,0:04:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的神奇之处便是无论受到何种冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游戏机都丝毫未伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前提是只要还有人在里面进行游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位先生的名字叫杰特·萨利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.07,0:04:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是游戏里的玩家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上 根据与他的签约
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.07,0:04:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个游戏机已转让给本次拍卖会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是金拿来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰特萨利留下了这样的契约书
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在本契约书记载的日期前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若我没完成这个游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 即使连我在内的7人还在进行游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也会向将这7套游戏连同机体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无偿捐与Southern Peace拍卖会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并将完成游戏的梦想寄于人才辈出的后辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遗憾的是 当我们拿到时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已有2人GAME OVER了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这便意味着玩家在现实世界也死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是伴随着死亡的危险游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请做好觉悟的观众竞拍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.15,0:05:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 起价是9亿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了10亿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.43,0:05:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了15亿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,105号 翻倍 30亿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.18,0:05:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,71号 再次翻倍 60亿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是大哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.18,0:05:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举起的手势代表金额啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主持人说出那之中最高的金额
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:58.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,16号 再次翻倍 120亿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,201号 再次翻倍 240亿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.72,0:06:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,16号 250亿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来大哥没能解析出「Greed Island」的ROM
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,71号 255亿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙 到底有多少钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.39,0:06:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,16号 一口气冲上305亿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:31.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,305亿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能完成这个游戏就行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我们是猎人...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想帮你们完成「Greed Island」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.56,0:06:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑 快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没看玩笑 真的是职业猎人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.86,0:07:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有执照吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.01,0:07:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 你没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:06.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在当铺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 现在...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 果然是说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.81,0:07:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 仅凭能进入这个会场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能看出你们不简单
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但 并不代表你们的话能全信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我确实是在雇佣猎人完成这个游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在没法雇佣你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟玩家人数有限
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 作战失败吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实说 我觉得不买游戏也行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想要的只是游戏中的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.87,0:07:50.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且拍得「Greed Island」的人当中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定也有寻找玩家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:07:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩家人数有限?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一张卡只能保存一个人的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算用转接插座
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一张卡最多也只能分给8个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.12,0:08:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 记忆卡的30个分区全都用于「Greed Island」了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.03,0:08:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有「Greed Island」的数据存档
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们以前玩过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.62,0:08:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 只有数据而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这样 那也...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那张卡是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从游戏机上拔出卡还需要另一个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:44.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然连戒指也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来有资格接受审查了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.82,0:08:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会使用念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让我看下炼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不能让他们玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候只会抱头鼠窜 最终难逃一死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都没有试过 怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:22.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试之后就晚了 小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要能干净利落死去还好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.84,0:09:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若一直苟延残喘着就难办了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种游戏是只要玩家还活在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便不可能重启或拔出记忆卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 新玩家进不去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.83,0:09:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所雇佣的猎人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,职业 业余包括在内共约100名在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但其中大半都已经放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:52.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃回到现实世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算一直生活在游戏中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 新玩家的筛选相当严格
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.59,0:10:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们所要求的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少要获得回到现实世界的物品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.19,0:10:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是有能力回来的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.91,0:10:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是说我们没有那种力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这家伙就能判断
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他是职业猎人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.54,0:10:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩过「Greed Island」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从经验来看 拿到回来的东西难度在中下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但以你们的念
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.05,0:10:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说拿到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就会GAME OVER
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,审查结束之后 我还会回到游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,审查?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是说你来审查玩家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日期是拍卖会的最后一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.47,0:10:47.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想参加
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前可要好好磨练你们的念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你说我们也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走 奇犽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.66,0:10:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎么拿到记忆卡的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 气死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对要参加审查
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.78,0:11:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,审查吗 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.51,0:11:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还用问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是盗贼 当然要盗过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回基地之后 玩玩看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里插着一张卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就意味着还能一人能玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.62,0:11:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用转接插座
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能让4个人玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那谁先开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前还半信半疑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.30,0:12:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游戏啊 你们要玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.19,0:12:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.53,0:12:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能会送命的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍卖会的目录上写的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然被对方说了那么过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那家伙说的也是实话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不过该进入下一阶段了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一阶段?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是必杀技啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:13:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷拉皮卡差不多和我们同时学习念的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 他却能和旅团不相上下的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为有必杀技
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.15,0:13:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷拉皮卡为了对付旅团
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:12.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到了近乎无敌的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.59,0:13:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其代价却背负着性命之忧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能这么走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风险要不大不小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且要符合自身系统
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不但实用 还能方便运用的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我们需要的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个个慢慢来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 最想要什么样的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.93,0:13:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么样的能力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 总有什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算笼统一点也行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之要很厉害的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也太笼统了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那先从自身系统开始考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是强化系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以能强化的能力比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 接下来就是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样强化你的哪一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.42,0:14:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你想好了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才来帮你想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗 是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杰 从今天开始我要进入必杀技特训了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就好好想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定只有我能通过审查
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.53,0:14:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不这样激将
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙很快就会走偏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想象自己的气和电融合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:15:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后是想象将储好的电一下释放
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,练成念
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以你们这种程度的念
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.44,0:15:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就会GAME OVER
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 绝对会让你见识见识
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干劲满满啊 小杰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.01,0:15:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷拉皮卡 痊愈了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烧已经退了 没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.41,0:15:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不像没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如果酷拉皮卡知道蜘蛛还在友克鑫的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.68,0:15:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有办法阻止他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.52,0:15:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 拍卖会怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.45,0:15:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你们看中了很贵的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.48,0:15:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 玩家选拔审查啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.06,0:15:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底进行了怎样的修行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.28,0:16:00.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定要具现化出锁链之后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是联想修行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.18,0:16:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭上眼睛 通过触摸感知
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.95,0:16:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想象出成百上千的画面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.87,0:16:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是不断的看着 品尝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,声音和味道也...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父告诉我只要玩锁链就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一段时间后 锁链被拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就能看到锁链的幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在幻想中能感受到它的沉重冰冷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及摩擦的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.82,0:16:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便自然而然能具现化出锁链
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.57,0:16:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除此之外 和你们一样 学习缠和炼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 酷拉皮卡 做我的师父吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是你 应该能帮我指出缺点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来 拍卖会期间就能阻止酷拉皮卡外出了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遗憾 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板明天要离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以我现在的立场 必须跟他一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要离开友克鑫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.37,0:17:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然挂念蜘蛛的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.70,0:17:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那之后都过了两天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕他们已经不在这里了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁教你念的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起我 问他不是更好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:33.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必杀技啊 真像你们的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.75,0:17:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从结论上说 强化系不需要必杀技
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.15,0:17:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为它是6个系统中 攻防比例最协调的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要用好缠和炼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也能有必杀技一般强大威力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 现在没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.72,0:17:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎样 我都要在4天后的审查...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.79,0:17:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杰 如果我是审查员
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:18:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是看到那种临时练成的必杀技的话 也会失望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.61,0:18:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懂了吗 小杰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不能模仿那个叫酷拉皮卡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我不说原因 光看他你也知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.66,0:18:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要模仿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.98,0:18:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的你也能发挥出足够特别的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.94,0:18:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.78,0:18:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.51,0:18:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好想想自己能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要这样 答案自然会出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.93,0:18:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提示
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了 给个提示
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你是真的很急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.77,0:18:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,焦躁是禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.63,0:18:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,踏踏实实才是捷径
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有期限 我也这么想...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.74,0:18:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法 大提示
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.39,0:18:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给那个叫乔治·杰拉人看的是普通的炼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.63,0:19:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次 把全部都给他看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:05.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗 你学会的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.38,0:19:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且是同时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学会的东西 全都同时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.02,0:19:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠 把气聚集在身体周围
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.96,0:19:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝 变成完全不释放气的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼 发出比通常多的大量气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后是 发
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 炼是发出气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝是不发出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把这些同时...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又卡住了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊 小杰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再磨磨蹭蹭 我可要甩下你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:05.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 出和不出怎么同时啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.98,0:20:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好想想自己能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云古老师指导我们如何运用念
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始只会缠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在战斗中受到很大的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.73,0:20:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也领悟了绝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 为了看破西索的技能学会了凝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.55,0:20:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凝?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.89,0:20:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 还有凝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凝是将气集中在眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现隐藏的气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.79,0:20:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 因为注意力全在眼部部分了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他部分的情况却很少注意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很少 但还有气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.01,0:20:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果把这些都封闭了 就能一切同时进行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 能行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.13,0:21:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.71,0:21:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是稍微松了下 气就散开了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.57,0:21:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样 把用炼增强的气集中在一个地方
